Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到處都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.26,0:02:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來博士是隨身攜帶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.97,0:02:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們慢了一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士恐怕已經
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.74,0:02:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你逃去哪裏\N我們一定會把它弄到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.05,0:02:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第八十三話\N由太郎歸國\N藏在影子下之黑騎士團的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.76,0:02:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣子出去練劍真的很沒勁耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.99,0:02:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個道場之前\N還曾經擁有五十個門徒耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼現在落沒成那樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.83,0:02:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀  以後劍道\N不知道會變成怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.14,0:02:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治新興文明開化政策\N把劍道徹底拋棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別連劍心你都講這種喪氣話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.58,0:02:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.35,0:02:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算憑我弱女子的一雙細手\N我也要把神谷活心流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.95,0:02:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弱女子的細手嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.38,0:03:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好比我的手還粗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.65,0:03:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我就是壯嘛 哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.03,0:03:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑\N完全不知道別人的辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.26,0:03:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦彌彥不可以說實話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的人是劍心你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了彌彥\N你搬這些進道場吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.07,0:03:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.48,0:03:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 怎麼不自己搬嘛\N受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助\N我們不在時有出什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.52,0:03:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.89,0:03:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 這個老頭的戰法太討厭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.36,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有外國來的客人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道是誰的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外國話！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你說說話呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.11,0:04:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了\N我來自德國我叫做漢斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.28,0:04:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.02,0:04:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,講日本話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是左之助 這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這招怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.05,0:04:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漢斯老爹不光會日語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,棋藝也很精呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經連敗五場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.76,0:04:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 將軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.16,0:04:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有認識什麼德國人耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.83,0:04:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是劍術高手 緋村劍心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我常聽到你的事跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.01,0:04:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.14,0:04:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害 你名揚德國了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不可能呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.78,0:04:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 你說明說明呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這招怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是將軍 把車吃下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.85,0:04:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是\N只有一個門生也是問題哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會是來踢館的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.20,0:05:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明神彌彥就當你對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是老樣子呆呆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.85,0:05:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看就知道了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老樣子沒變的人是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.16,0:05:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的右手呢 傷好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.20,0:05:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別用問的 用這個試試怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我來當你對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩人很快就打起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.95,0:05:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是跟由太郎同行的人\N左之助你怎麼不早說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.92,0:05:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你剛剛說什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.15,0:05:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還記得嗎 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.06,0:05:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們倆還沒分出高低呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.20,0:06:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當然記得\N我到德國還繼續練劍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那正好 看招 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.24,0:06:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 這就是真正的劍術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣跟打架差不多\N喂！你們兩個！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了啦 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩人很久沒碰面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.76,0:06:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.39,0:06:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們口是心非 高興得很呢\N就讓他們打吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.97,0:06:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 彌彥 你認輸了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼 還早呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.57,0:06:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.01,0:06:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漢斯老爹沒問題吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太興奮血壓會升高的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也擔心著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.71,0:07:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾達斯中尉歡迎光臨日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.78,0:07:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是慶祝你們平安抵達的派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就放鬆下來享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.02,0:07:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魯德爾公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.15,0:07:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有件事我要跟你談談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請把人遣走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼 要講話隨時都行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.03,0:07:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來來 先乾一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.83,0:07:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也喝呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的酒醒了吧 公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音樂停止演奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.24,0:07:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 非常抱歉\N今夜派對到此結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.82,0:08:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我再找機會賠罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.33,0:08:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個以後再忙\N你們快滾 還不快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.57,0:08:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們德意志帝國的精英軍官\N找遠東小島的公司想談什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我單刀直入明講好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.78,0:08:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天起 德意志公司館\N劃入我們的指揮範圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.72,0:08:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實也沒啥大變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就假裝沒看見也不提此事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就當做跟以前一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.00,0:08:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你還想平安回祖國的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.33,0:08:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什麼資格提這要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.57,0:08:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你被降級到邊境來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好歹應該還知道這徽章吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.91,0:09:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你們是黑騎士團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.08,0:09:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了慎重起見 我忠告你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.28,0:09:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們發誓忠誠的對象\N不是德意志帝國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.12,0:09:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是偉大的指導者 麥斯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑騎士團為什麼來日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.43,0:09:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了你的人身安全\N你最好少刺探消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是我要你幫我調查東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.24,0:09:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個男人應該有來日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.14,0:09:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還和日本小男孩在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.78,0:09:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你查出他們的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漢斯博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他應該很累了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.00,0:10:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 在船上\N他也一直在畫那奇怪地圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.74,0:10:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為由太郎的右手動手術的\N原來是那位漢斯博士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.08,0:10:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真看不出來 那個老爹\N竟然是那麼高明的大夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.45,0:10:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實他不用去住飯店\N住我們這裏就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎的傷治好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.39,0:10:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要開個慶祝宴\N慶祝他入門呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.20,0:10:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也對\N我正想找機會答謝漢斯博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.30,0:10:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去紅牛怎麼樣\N明天那裏放煙火呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.37,0:10:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先聲明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.54,0:10:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不打算慶祝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.11,0:10:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥真是 還說負氣話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.54,0:10:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是若是要吃牛肉火鍋\N就另當別論了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.98,0:10:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也全力贊成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 你就會找理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.69,0:10:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到地圖以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.69,0:10:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直受到不明人士跟蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.94,0:11:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了以防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.24,0:11:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必需把這個留下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則未來不知會發生什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.68,0:11:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.18,0:11:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.19,0:11:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 不知不覺大聲吼你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.53,0:11:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要道歉的人是我呀 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.70,0:11:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.63,0:11:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天還要到道場練劍吧\N你早點去睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腰再用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.82,0:11:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 再揮一百下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.66,0:12:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.90,0:12:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開壺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二加六是雙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.17,0:12:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.04,0:12:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來再畫一筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.37,0:12:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來一次 這次我不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 要來幾次都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開壺！這次是雙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我賭單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.28,0:12:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.72,0:12:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來 由太郎 恭喜你的傷好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有恭喜你入門神谷活心流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.33,0:12:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是大喜事呀\N今天我們大大慶祝一番吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.00,0:12:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.77,0:12:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是頭號弟子\N你是二號別忘記這一點哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.44,0:12:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這沒有關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這是對前輩的態度嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.91,0:12:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你算什麼前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.95,0:12:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.65,0:13:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你們倆個別過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.05,0:13:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是由太郎的心情\N比在德國時開朗呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.29,0:13:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 我們吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.82,0:13:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.29,0:13:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你們再打下去\N肉會被左之助全部吃光哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.47,0:13:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 你太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.07,0:13:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.32,0:13:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來只好問他本人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.69,0:13:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎的右手傷勢很重的\N能夠完全治好真了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是西醫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.53,0:13:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漢斯博士\N在德國是出名的醫學博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.17,0:13:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且跟德國醫學比起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.34,0:13:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本醫學不知落後幾十年\N不 好幾百年呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.71,0:14:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可不能讓小惠聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.95,0:14:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我要更努力讀書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.48,0:14:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用從博士那裏學來的醫術\N成為拯救日本人的醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.99,0:14:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對西方人那麼崇拜\N虧你還是武士的後代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.96,0:14:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼要打嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.76,0:14:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.37,0:14:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.20,0:14:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拯救病苦的人們\N是不分西方或東方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.84,0:14:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才研究東方的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.37,0:14:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也因此才跟你熟悉起來的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漢斯博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.68,0:14:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪不得棋藝跟擲骰子\N都那麼精啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.28,0:14:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了\N既然這樣我不再手下留情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天我一定跟你分出勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 比幾次都沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.79,0:14:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助還沒學乖呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.96,0:14:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼由太郎\N明天也在道場見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.90,0:14:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天我一定跟你分出勝負\N你可別偷懶哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.94,0:15:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.94,0:15:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.94,0:15:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很煩耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活該！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.58,0:15:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我們告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安\N晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.88,0:15:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 去看完煙火就回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅豆湯不吃了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.72,0:15:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎長大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.63,0:15:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還立志成為醫生來救許多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.14,0:15:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是某某人\N可以向他看齊就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.57,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連阿薰都替由太郎講話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎靠醫術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.51,0:15:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你靠劍術救人就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像劍心那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.95,0:15:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 我才不會輸給由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.79,0:15:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩 就是這個志氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.16,0:15:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.96,0:15:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.73,0:16:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷道場的人都是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.50,0:16:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了彌彥以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.97,0:16:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我看來\N彌彥跟你是好朋友哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.45,0:16:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漢斯博士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.32,0:16:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們為了追你\N大老遠跑過來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.49,0:16:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祖國的軍人找我有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.53,0:16:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那個東西交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.33,0:16:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個東西？你在講什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你帶在身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.67,0:16:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不想死在遙遠的異鄉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.74,0:16:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 乖乖聽話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.05,0:16:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不是普通軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.85,0:16:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是漢斯博士\N很有觀察力嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難不成…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.99,0:17:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.03,0:17:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎 快點逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣 博士 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別囉嗦 聽我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.29,0:17:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉 是地圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情辦完了 給他死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.53,0:17:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.90,0:17:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.70,0:17:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也想死嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.98,0:18:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准你們碰這孩子一根汗毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.75,0:18:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太驚人了 沒想到\N這偏遠地方還會有劍術高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.16,0:18:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是傳說中的武士嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.63,0:18:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷茲少尉 這裏交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.18,0:18:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就當你對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.42,0:18:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修奈特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修奈特 撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.01,0:18:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情辦完了 走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.35,0:19:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎 你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.42,0:19:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士呢 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.42,0:19:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過份 為什麼對博士做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.39,0:19:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漢斯博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.96,0:19:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之 趕快帶去玄齊大夫那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.77,0:19:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡…我跟著卻沒能保護他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.41,0:19:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.88,0:19:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士 我是由太郎 我在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.48,0:19:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原諒我…我把你捲入危險當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.52,0:19:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來日本\N其實是為了尋找某個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.40,0:19:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某個地方？\N跟被奪走的地圖有關嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.50,0:19:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為了以防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.57,0:20:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把線索跟地圖分開來\N藏在神谷道場的走廊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.41,0:20:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.94,0:20:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護神聖的靈藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.91,0:20:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕不能落入他們手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士 振作一點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.48,0:20:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大夫 手術準備完畢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.95,0:20:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.39,0:20:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給我跟玄齊大夫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一定會救他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.41,0:20:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算萬一日本政府展開行動\N你們也不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.31,0:20:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要得到這個\N剩下的就是遲早的問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.38,0:20:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼 這個糟老頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.85,0:20:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不趕快退開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.59,0:20:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.96,0:21:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有地圖\N是找不到你們要找的東西的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.13,0:21:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.03,0:21:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.55,0:21:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奸雄識奸雄\N你們也不用覺得可疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.98,0:21:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問你是誰呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.49,0:21:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真田忍者頭目\N洩矢御沙薙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.46,0:21:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 那真是失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.53,0:21:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是信奉騎士道的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.16,0:21:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,容我為剛才\N對淑女的失禮行為道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.83,0:21:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果可能\N我想請教先前那段話的下文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.84,0:21:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.85,0:21:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了 是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.42,0:22:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是博士的筆記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.16,0:22:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼 看來像普通石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.93,0:22:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎 漢斯博士說的\N神聖的靈藥是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.43,0:22:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈藥是指藥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.77,0:22:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.10,0:22:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,線索只有這兩個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.41,0:22:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.75,0:22:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會盡我的微薄之力幫助你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.18,0:22:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 你別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.28,0:22:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝

